headline: Equifax Introduces Quarterly Market Pulse Index to Provide Insights Into the Financial State of U.S. Consumers
summary: Equifax® (NYSE: EFX) today released its inaugural Market Pulse Index report – a first-of-its-kind aggregated view of the financial state of U.S. consumers. Offering a multidimensional view of U.S. consumer finances, the Market Pulse Index is designed to highlight how key financial components interact at a population or segment level and evolve over time and among changing economic circumstances. headline: 3 Mid-Cap Stocks Walking a Fine Line
summary: Mid-cap stocks often strike the right balance between having proven business models and market opportunities that can support $100 billion corporations. However, they face intense competition from scaled industry giants and can be disrupted by new innovative players vying for a slice of the pie.
